，指小食會當日員工只可在5款小食中任選2款，5款小食包括4粒燒賣、4粒魚蛋、1湯匙粟米、一隻茶葉蛋以及一隻雞翼，並非想像的小食「自助餐」，她更笑指，不少傳媒的圖片都顯示是一大碗「燒賣魚蛋」，根本是「錯曬」！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>有網民笑指，小食會「好似啲Promotion咁，要Upload IG、Like埋FB先有得食」；亦有人表示：「感受到醫護人員那一股怨氣！」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2261904/屯院「小食打氣」小食5選2包括1湯匙粟米%E3%80%80前線斥：忙到爆仍被迫充撐場面\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2261904%2F%E5%B1%AF%E9%99%A2%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E9%A3%9F%E6%89%93%E6%B0%A3%E3%80%8D%E5%B0%8F%E9%A3%9F5%E9%81%B82%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC1%E6%B9%AF%E5%8C%99%E7%B2%9F%E7%B1%B3%25E3%2580%2580%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%A5%EF%BC%9A%E5%BF%99%E5%88%B0%E7%88%86%E4%BB%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%BF%AB%E5%85%85%E6%92%90%E5%A0%B4%E9%9D%A2&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=19574ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2261904/屯院「小食打氣」小食5選2包括1湯匙粟米%E3%80%80前線斥：忙到爆仍被迫充撐場面</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T15:54:39.000Z","msg":"真係好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80995933f9af20764fce9234d6926a6c043fc0ce","tid":1834921,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:00:43.000Z","msg":"加入工會<br />\n<br />\nHAEA"},{"pid":"0b7d64afd8a14d3504e6088571860721d43d3fe4","tid":1834921,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"醫護平時都是醫傷風感冒，有燒賣食咪唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7e101bfe31c7a920ea5a71d54ec93e66c25edc","tid":1834921,"uid":172668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"醫護保護好自己啦<br />\n而家睇個勢要接一班蝗蟲<br />\n<br />\n如果你話要罷工既<br />\n我接受"},{"pid":"a1ddac473abee6b380e2530f73acaef00344f925","tid":1834921,"uid":25973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b7d64afd8a14d3504e6088571860721d43d3fe4","tid":1834921,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"醫護平時都是醫傷風感冒，有燒賣食咪